  "synopsis": "Obsessed with their rather ordinary classmate Ken Kirio, high school students Aimi Miyoshi and Nami Sometani form a peculiar friendship. Every time the girls hang out, they talk about Kirio and fantasize about interacting with the boy they usually just observe from afar. Aimi and Nami are mostly satisfied with the status quo, but they occasionally cannot help but be jealous of those who get to be near their crush—though this still rarely leads them to approach him directly.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]",
